Let's try something else.

239
00:21:13,833 --> 00:21:14,833
A new method.

240
00:21:42,250 --> 00:21:43,458
It's the wind.

241
00:21:53,541 --> 00:21:54,750
Shit.

242
00:21:57,166 --> 00:21:58,083
Damn! Wee!

