263
00:25:01,375 --> 00:25:04,666
You made me hold
all this. You're holding one thing.

264
00:25:12,791 --> 00:25:13,791
Which way now?

265
00:25:23,625 --> 00:25:25,416
-Left.
-Sure. You go first.

266
00:25:38,166 --> 00:25:39,000
Hey.

