that something was wrong?

830
01:22:20,916 --> 01:22:21,791
Or maybe

831
01:22:23,125 --> 01:22:24,541
he tried to tell me,

832
01:22:25,833 --> 01:22:27,083
but I didn't listen.

833
01:22:27,750 --> 01:22:29,416
Didn't I pay attention or…

834
01:22:30,458 --> 01:22:33,500
What was wrong?
Was I such an awful girlfriend?

835
01:22:35,000 --> 01:22:39,250
Was I so shitty that I didn't know
what was wrong with my boyfriend?

836
01:22:40,625 --> 01:22:41,833
What was wrong?

837
01:22:43,125 --> 01:22:44,000
Breathe, Mai.

838
01:22:45,916 --> 01:22:46,750
I mean, look.

839
01:22:47,416 --> 01:22:49,708
Even my boyfriend's password.

840
01:22:51,250 --> 01:22:55,333
-I don't even know it, shit!
-Mai.

841
01:23:08,000 --> 01:23:13,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)
It's alright.

842
01:23:41,041 --> 01:23:42,875
I'll take this to my friend.

843
01:23:42,958 --> 01:23:44,375
We might unlock it tonight.

844
01:23:54,291 --> 01:23:55,416
What the fuck, man?

845
01:23:56,666 --> 01:24:00,041
Didn't we agree
that no one could know about the research?

846
01:24:00,583 --> 01:24:03,291
If Mai finds out,
she'll tell someone for sure.

847
01:24:03,833 --> 01:24:06,041
What happens to it then? Do you care?

848
01:24:21,625 --> 01:24:22,916
You were MIA so long.

849
01:24:23,875 --> 01:24:26,416
You came back to tell your girl the truth?

850
01:24:26,500 --> 01:24:27,916
I called for you, remember?

851
01:24:29,708 --> 01:24:30,916
Why didn't you come?

852
01:24:33,916 --> 01:24:36,333
Do you still care about what we're doing?

853
01:24:37,541 --> 01:24:38,375
Huh?

854
01:24:48,000 --> 01:24:53,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)
Forget her!
Let her feel guilty. It won't kill her.

855
01:25:14,291 --> 01:25:15,125
Whoa!

856
01:25:31,708 --> 01:25:32,541
Shit!

857
01:25:37,333 --> 01:25:39,833
Hello? Can anyone hear me?

858
01:25:42,000 --> 01:25:47,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)
The elevator's stuck
on the 13th floor. Please help me.
Hello? Can anyone hear me?

859
01:25:51,708 --> 01:25:52,541
Shit.

860
01:27:13,833 --> 01:27:15,083
It's hot.

861
01:27:16,916 --> 01:27:19,416
So you'll tell me the truth about Gla?

862
01:27:20,250 --> 01:27:21,583
You found out more?

863
01:27:22,375 --> 01:27:23,208
Yep.

864
01:27:25,416 --> 01:27:27,000
I asked you to meet me here

865
01:27:29,000 --> 01:27:30,833
so you could see for yourself.

866
01:27:32,208 --> 01:27:33,708
You'll understand it all.

867
01:27:35,541 --> 01:27:37,625
I have to go and prepare something.

868
01:27:38,583 --> 01:27:39,416
I'll be back.

869
01:27:57,083 --> 01:27:58,666
At Mai's condo yesterday,

870
01:27:59,208 --> 01:28:02,583
I learned of another way
to boost the spirit's power.

871
01:28:03,333 --> 01:28:10,000
ENERGY = WORRIES

872
01:28:13,333 --> 01:28:16,791
ENERGY = WORRIES / VENGEANCE

873
01:29:21,625 --> 01:29:27,250
Oh! Wow! I thought
that you weren't coming back anymore!

874
01:29:29,208 --> 01:29:30,166
How's the beach?

875
01:29:31,375 --> 01:29:32,208
Huh?

876
01:29:38,666 --> 01:29:40,416
Experiment log number 103.

877
01:29:40,500 --> 01:29:43,041
I decided to redesign
the experiment again.

878
01:29:43,583 --> 01:29:46,000
This time, I'm sure that it will succeed.

879
01:29:50,625 --> 01:29:51,458
So close now.

880
01:29:52,625 --> 01:29:55,125
I'm this close to making the ghost appear.

881
01:30:13,625 --> 01:30:14,458
Hey!

882
01:30:20,875 --> 01:30:22,166
You said it yourself.

883
01:30:23,333 --> 01:30:26,125
You want Mai to know
about the experiment. Look!

884
01:30:28,500 --> 01:30:30,125
I got her to participate.

885
01:30:31,791 --> 01:30:32,750
Isn't this good?

886
01:30:36,458 --> 01:30:37,708
You want this, right?

887
01:30:42,000 --> 01:30:47,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)
Hey!

888
01:30:54,041 --> 01:30:55,666
Deep down, you know, right?

889
01:30:57,375 --> 01:30:58,208
The truth is

890
01:30:59,250 --> 01:31:00,166
I like Mai too.

891
01:31:02,000 --> 01:31:02,833
Oh, right.

892
01:31:04,083 --> 01:31:05,625
I forgot that you're dead.

893
01:31:06,291 --> 01:31:07,291
Shit. Sorry, man.

894
01:31:10,583 --> 01:31:12,000
You mind if I take Mai

895
01:31:12,541 --> 01:31:13,375
for myself?

896
01:31:18,000 --> 01:31:23,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

897
01:31:39,166 --> 01:31:40,083
Where are you?

898
01:31:40,166 --> 01:31:41,000
Tell me.

899
01:31:43,000 --> 01:31:48,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)
Where are you?
So close. We're this close.

900
01:31:59,250 --> 01:32:02,666
GHOSTS = ?

901
01:32:25,000 --> 01:32:30,000
Upcoming jump scare (Major)

902
01:32:32,958 --> 01:32:33,791
Hey!

903
01:32:35,333 --> 01:32:36,166
Gla!

904
01:32:37,500 --> 01:32:39,041
You can show yourself now.

905
01:32:41,541 --> 01:32:42,500
Can you hear me?

906
01:32:43,583 --> 01:32:45,458
We succeeded, damn it!

907
01:32:46,000 --> 01:32:51,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

908
01:32:57,000 --> 01:33:02,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

909
01:33:11,000 --> 01:33:16,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

910
01:34:28,000 --> 01:34:33,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

911
01:34:52,125 --> 01:34:55,166
Hell yeah, we're on the right track!

912
01:35:28,541 --> 01:35:29,375
Shit.

913
01:35:41,666 --> 01:35:43,041
Experiment log

914
01:35:44,666 --> 01:35:46,291
number 104.

915
01:35:47,166 --> 01:35:48,583
The results show that…

916
01:35:51,708 --> 01:35:53,000
using his girlfriend

917
01:35:54,791 --> 01:35:57,083
to trigger negative emotions…

918
01:36:00,291 --> 01:36:03,041
made the spirit of Dr. Arjong…

919
01:36:07,416 --> 01:36:09,958
show his true form for the first time.

920
01:36:10,833 --> 01:36:13,833
This is our first time
seeing his "Northern Lights."

921
01:36:26,041 --> 01:36:26,958
Fuck you, Gla!

922
01:36:27,583 --> 01:36:28,416
Not so hard!

923
01:36:31,916 --> 01:36:33,375
Now I know what to do.

924
01:36:34,125 --> 01:36:36,125
Now, if you wanna expose the truth

925
01:36:36,208 --> 01:36:37,500
or deal with someone,

926
01:36:37,583 --> 01:36:39,625
I'll set it up. Maybe next time,

927
01:36:40,166 --> 01:36:41,291
I'll get your sis--

928
01:36:58,833 --> 01:36:59,666
Hey!

929
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:10,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

930
01:38:06,375 --> 01:38:07,541
Hey--

931
01:38:09,708 --> 01:38:11,541
You can get back in your body?

932
01:38:13,583 --> 01:38:14,416
Damn, this is

933
01:38:15,750 --> 01:38:17,375
even more than we expected.

934
01:38:18,208 --> 01:38:21,166
If I can keep you
in this form for everyone to see…

935
01:38:24,958 --> 01:38:27,000
Our experiment is coming together!

936
01:38:29,708 --> 01:38:30,708
I must film this.

937
01:38:32,291 --> 01:38:33,416
Let me record this.

938
01:38:36,000 --> 01:38:41,000
Upcoming jump scare (Minor)

939
01:38:51,000 --> 01:38:52,625
Wasn't it you who told me…

940
01:38:56,041 --> 01:38:57,958
"If we really want the truth,

941
01:39:00,708 --> 01:39:02,375
we must cross the line"?

942
01:39:09,458 --> 01:39:10,916
When you shot yourself…

943
01:39:13,541 --> 01:39:16,333
you didn't even think
of your mom, or Gift,

944
01:39:16,875 --> 01:39:18,000
or even Mai at all!

945
01:39:20,958 --> 01:39:24,416
You really want to go
to your beloved  beach?

946
01:39:25,750 --> 01:39:26,791
I won't let you.

947
01:39:28,583 --> 01:39:30,291
We've come this far already.

948
01:39:31,041 --> 01:39:32,291
I have to finish it.

949
01:39:34,083 --> 01:39:35,583
Whatever shit I must do,

950
01:39:36,291 --> 01:39:37,125
I will do it!

951
01:40:01,083 --> 01:40:02,083
Whoa!

952
01:41:25,166 --> 01:41:26,875
How did we get to this point?

953
01:41:33,250 --> 01:41:34,083
Gla.

954
01:41:40,541 --> 01:41:41,875
I've become a monster.

955
01:41:44,583 --> 01:41:46,875
And I'm turning you into one too.

956
01:41:53,125 --> 01:41:54,250
Wee.

957
01:41:55,500 --> 01:41:56,333
Thanks, man.

958
01:41:57,791 --> 01:41:58,916
You kept your word.

959
01:42:00,541 --> 01:42:01,791
Now you must stop.

960
01:42:03,625 --> 01:42:04,458
No way, Gla.

961
01:42:06,750 --> 01:42:07,916
If you don't stop,

962
01:42:09,833 --> 01:42:12,500
what other evil things
will you do for the experiment?

963
01:42:20,666 --> 01:42:22,583
But we've come this far already.

964
01:42:24,916 --> 01:42:26,208
We're almost there.

965
01:42:27,000 --> 01:42:28,250
To reach this point,

966
01:42:30,458 --> 01:42:32,041
what did you have to sacrifice?

967
01:42:36,666 --> 01:42:38,916
I've hurt enough people around me.

968
01:42:42,916 --> 01:42:44,416
Everything must stop here.

969
01:42:52,125 --> 01:42:54,833
Are you telling me
to let you die for free?

970
01:43:08,333 --> 01:43:09,166
Wee…

971
01:43:11,666 --> 01:43:13,166
you did your best for me…

972
01:43:15,250 --> 01:43:16,083
for your mom,

973
01:43:17,958 --> 01:43:19,375
and for this experiment.

974
01:43:22,041 --> 01:43:23,958
You don't have to feel guilty anymore.

975
01:43:49,208 --> 01:43:50,208
I have to go now.

976
01:43:53,083 --> 01:43:54,291
My journey goes on.

977
01:44:00,041 --> 01:44:00,875
Damn you, Gla!

978
01:45:11,500 --> 01:45:12,333
Gla!

979
01:45:27,041 --> 01:45:29,291
Sir, everything that happened

980
01:45:29,375 --> 01:45:32,166
was caused by his severe emotional trauma.

981
01:45:32,250 --> 01:45:33,916
after the loss of his mother

982
01:45:34,958 --> 01:45:36,500
and his friend's suicide.

983
01:45:38,833 --> 01:45:41,333
I know you want to protect your resident.

984
01:45:43,000 --> 01:45:44,666
But the Council must investigate.

985
01:45:46,000 --> 01:45:47,666
He may never practice again.

986
01:46:32,916 --> 01:46:36,083
In my first year, I once asked Gla

987
01:46:37,125 --> 01:46:39,500
why he was so fascinated with science.

988
01:46:42,000 --> 01:46:42,875
He told me

989
01:46:43,666 --> 01:46:45,166
that every day we live

990
01:46:45,750 --> 01:46:47,666
is like a science experiment.

991
01:46:50,708 --> 01:46:51,875
We set hypotheses

992
01:46:52,583 --> 01:46:54,333
and our expectations.

993
01:46:56,750 --> 01:46:58,666
We try to control the variables.

994
01:47:02,083 --> 01:47:04,750
Some are controllable. Some aren't.

995
01:47:08,916 --> 01:47:10,583
Sometimes what's been done

996
01:47:11,875 --> 01:47:13,541
is almost completely ruined.

997
01:47:20,791 --> 01:47:22,458
Whatever the result is…

998
01:47:28,458 --> 01:47:30,458
we still learn something from it,

999
01:47:32,000 --> 01:47:33,125
more or less.

1000
01:47:33,208 --> 01:47:35,958
NORTHERN LIGHTS QUEST

1001
01:47:42,416 --> 01:47:45,666
NORTHERN LIGHTS QUEST

1002
01:48:03,916 --> 01:48:05,625
I got the laptop unlocked.

1003
01:48:15,250 --> 01:48:16,416
Mai, listen…

1004
01:48:22,833 --> 01:48:23,666
That night--

1005
01:48:23,750 --> 01:48:25,875
Wee. You don't have to say anything.

1006
01:48:28,333 --> 01:48:29,541
I talked to Namo.

1007
01:48:31,083 --> 01:48:35,250
I know. Back then,
you weren't really emotionally stable.

1008
01:48:39,541 --> 01:48:40,500
And maybe…

1009
01:48:43,291 --> 01:48:45,541
I wasn't in my right mind yet either.

1010
01:48:49,000 --> 01:48:49,875
You know what?

1011
01:48:51,333 --> 01:48:53,666
The night I fell asleep in your office,

1012
01:48:55,583 --> 01:48:56,416
I think…

1013
01:48:59,041 --> 01:49:00,375
Gla came to see me.

1014
01:49:05,583 --> 01:49:06,458
In my dream,

1015
01:49:07,500 --> 01:49:08,875
we were at the seaside.

1016
01:49:12,250 --> 01:49:14,583
But I don't know where exactly.

1017
01:49:49,750 --> 01:49:52,250
In my dream, I didn't say anything to him.

1018
01:49:56,250 --> 01:49:57,958
Just seeing him happy

1019
01:50:01,000 --> 01:50:02,666
was enough to make me so happy.

1020
01:50:18,875 --> 01:50:19,708
Hey, Wee.

1021
01:50:21,375 --> 01:50:22,208
In my dream,

1022
01:50:24,666 --> 01:50:26,791
Gla was holding this magazine.

1023
01:50:28,333 --> 01:50:30,458
On the cover was a photo of you two.

1024
01:50:58,583 --> 01:50:59,791
Wee.

1025
01:51:03,791 --> 01:51:04,916
I'm jealous of you.

1026
01:51:07,833 --> 01:51:09,083
You still have a chance.

1027
01:51:16,541 --> 01:51:18,416
Live your life for the both of us.

1028
01:51:25,791 --> 01:51:26,916
I think he's right.

1029
01:51:30,208 --> 01:51:31,833
We just have to learn from it.

1030
01:51:36,666 --> 01:51:37,791
As long as we live,

1031
01:51:38,458 --> 01:51:41,250
we must continue
our experiments until the end.

